ruling: - If the Normal Monster Special Summoned by [[Swing of Memories]] is flipped face-down, it will not be destroyed during the End Phase. Even if the Normal Monster is flipped face-up during the same turn, it will not be destroyed during the End Phase.

- If the Normal Monster Special Summoned by [[Swing of Memories]] is removed from play with [[Interdimensional Matter Transporter]], it will not be destroyed during the End Phase even after it is returned to the field.
